br />\n<br />\n曲還曲 見撚到你啲emoji 都唔撚想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba89672d0029e5ad9c89e0d175b1f6c271849f5","tid":1429213,"uid":289857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"曲到圓啊屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d961bfcfe138588cff0ba393f4bc06b51263fd4","tid":1429213,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"加返個<br />\n以藍制藍，以紅制紅"},{"pid":"ef23b58531701603e1d6a1975cf38772a0347716","tid":1429213,"uid":281401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"曲得太低層次"},{"pid":"e25756f3cc146e0249727b84d9c0d5617c0eed3d","tid":1429213,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"岩呀岩呀<br />\n聽日就出老解一國一制炸撚晒D飛機同船<br />\n全部香港人要強制剪非中國PASSPORT<br />\n齊齊享大灣區繁榮"}]}